Package uk.org.mygrid.cagrid.domain.ncbiblast

Class Summary
Alignment An alignment between the query sequence and match sequence.
NCBIBlastInput Represents an input to the Taverna-wrapped NCBI BLAST service that taverna will convert and actually invoke the service.
NCBIBlastInputParameters Input parameters for the NCBI BLAST job.
NCBIBlastJob  
NCBIBlastOutput This is an output from the Taverna-wrapped InterProScan service that Taverna will convert and pass back to caGrid client.
NCBIBlastService Represents Taverbna-wrapping of the NCBI BLAST service to be used by caGrid clients.
SequenceFragment A protein or nucleotide sequence fragment (where the similarity was found in).
SequenceSimilarity Represents a similarity match in the sequence database.
